	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you are wanting to med, go into the center of the maze. You can sit and med there without ever having a problem. As long as nothing is aggroed onto you before you go in, you'll be fine.<br><br>Also, when by the gazebo, be careful with the pathing. If you dart down the wall behind the hedge, the pathing will take the mob around the hedge the long way and probably pick up extra friends on the way to slice and pound on you. <br><br>Just my two coppers. I love Unrest, a great place for paladins and clerics IMO.<br>&nbsp;<br>Tenser - Mighty Enchanter<br>Hasan - The Erudite Paladin</td></tr>
